pulseview (0.4.0-1) experimental; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release.
    + Remove GCC 6 patch now included upstream.
    + Now requires libsigrok (>= 0.5.0), libsigrokdecode (>= 0.5.0),
      libglibmm-2.4-dev (>= 2.28.0), qtbase5-dev, qtbase5-dev-tools,
      libqt5svg5-dev, libboost-test-dev
    + Update icon from sigrok-logo-notext.png to pulseview.png
    + Update debian/copyright
    + Remove Debian specific .desktop in favour of upstream version
  * Move maintenance to Debian Electronics Packaging Team (Closes: #852833)
  * Standards-Version: 4.0.1
    + Change priority to optional

 -- Jonathan McDowell <noodles@earth.li>  Fri, 01 Sep 2017 19:29:47 +0100

